{"tid":2209891,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"（鬼節）有無巴打試過突然發好高燒？","createTime":"2020-09-20T03:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:48:13.000Z","uid":97374,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"353d2fb42a5cdd1211f4393904028186ad417437","tid":2209891,"uid":97374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"前排鬼節，<br />\n我去過一個朋友既屋企 天光先走<br />\n咁佢個屋苑好似有過兇案 <br />\n過左幾日都無野<br />\n有日我下午出去行街 都好有精神 正正常常<br />\n夜晚番到屋企5 6 點 做運動 覺得突然體力好差咁<br />\n然後7 8 點<br />\n突然發燒 頭痛頭暈周身痛燒上近39 度 （量左好多次）<br />\n然後就係床休息 訓左10 幾個鐘 都唔退燒<br />\n跟住拎感冒藥頂住 都斷斷續續係床訓左就快48 個鐘 <br />\n先退燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且完全無其他感冒症狀"},{"pid":"4a1e4cc1b43562156244343a140d898545d52e81","tid":2209891,"uid":195915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"俾鬼整"},{"pid":"c16e2e7e5723658e797d11b8fd51476de40e3737","tid":2209891,"uid":88663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"細菌/病毒/寄生蟲感染"},{"pid":"e10e70bef482b9817f38685655c5682aa0762793","tid":2209891,"uid":40445,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"有樣野叫睇醫生"},{"pid":"fa5a293832119e022d8bcd5b4e5f058b1b98470d","tid":2209891,"uid":51761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會係中武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3a07d83a96f4944b2adb58bbe78626fa4cb806","tid":2209891,"uid":97374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5a293832119e022d8bcd5b4e5f058b1b98470d","tid":2209891,"uid":51761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會係中武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"真係唔知，但又好似唔中完全無其他武肺症狀 <br />\n同埋個突發性好似一個鐘前仲可以跳舞，一個鐘後突然燒到郁唔到咁"},{"pid":"7d59bf61ba74b2038b6af3d2d56ab9d75848bffe","tid":2209891,"uid":9737